                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " High-purity germanium detector GCD-20180 was",
                "used. The diameter, length and sensitive volume of the",
                "germanium crystal were 51.7 mm, 49.05 mm and 101.2 cm3,",
                "respectively. The detector resolution at 1.33 MeV was",
                "1.8 keV."
              ]
